<subSubSection id="C0A8E3AE18AD719D8EEB16E6E6C53F3C" pageId="0" pageNumber="52190" type="notes">
<paragraph id="1B900E63D835F1FCECBB72D35CFBDAA1" pageId="0" pageNumber="52190">Notes</paragraph>
<paragraph id="F08C2C65AE11F53CA8E2621432017F99" pageId="0" pageNumber="52190">
<taxonomicName id="B1F267EF0CDD70DD28EB368881F1EDF6" authority="Hausmann, 1994" authorityName="Exposito" authorityYear="2005" class="Insecta" family="Geometridae" genus="Kuchleria" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Kuchleria garciapitai" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="0" pageNumber="52190" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="garciapitai">
<emphasis id="20D96A0BF4A10B311F3417B303D51189" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="52190">Kuchleria garciapitai</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
was designated a junior synonym of 
<taxonomicName id="5B5626F5CEF6A9E2A0EB3F1819A70EB6" genus="K." lsidName="K. insignata" pageId="0" pageNumber="52190" rank="species" species="insignata">
<emphasis id="CEFBF07EE32DCB7D24D3CA0CA3C5FD31" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="52190">K. insignata</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
by 
<bibRefCitation id="681CEB3DB5C7E7A1AE9B2F9195F10507" author="Leraut, P" journalOrPublisher="NAP Editions, Paris" pageId="0" pageNumber="52190" refId="B5536812" refString="Leraut, P, 2009. Moths of Europe-Volume 2: Geometrid moths. NAP Editions, Paris" title="Moths of Europe-Volume 2: Geometrid moths." year="2009">Leraut (2009)</bibRefCitation>
. In the same publication, 
<bibRefCitation id="467993616C008F06CDB549AB95C8D6B8" author="Leraut, P" journalOrPublisher="NAP Editions, Paris" pageId="0" pageNumber="52190" refId="B5536812" refString="Leraut, P, 2009. Moths of Europe-Volume 2: Geometrid moths. NAP Editions, Paris" title="Moths of Europe-Volume 2: Geometrid moths." year="2009">Leraut (2009)</bibRefCitation>
claimed that 
<taxonomicName id="5F56B3FBEA76C20BCF348B44066AAFBE" genus="K." lsidName="K. insignata" pageId="0" pageNumber="52190" rank="species" species="insignata">
<emphasis id="C2B186DE608E83711567A823F3C6254E" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="52190">K. insignata</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
was a &quot;synonym or subspecies&quot; of 
<taxonomicName id="113FE555BDD8918B99A148F856C8BFD1" authority="Hausmann, 1994" authorityName="Hausmann" authorityYear="1994" baseAuthorityName="Thierry-Mieg" baseAuthorityYear="1893" class="Insecta" family="Geometridae" genus="Kuchleria" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Kuchleria menadiara" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="0" pageNumber="52190" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="menadiara">
<emphasis id="0303D0367EAA414E240F5DB2EBF34135" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="52190">Kuchleria menadiara</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
Thierry-Mieg, 1893. 
<bibRefCitation id="BC902DA3574CB47B797B8BD1FF31901F" author="Mueller, B" journalOrPublisher="Brill, Leiden" pageId="0" pageNumber="52190" refId="B5536891" refString="Mueller, B, Erlacher, S, Hausmann, A, Rajaei, H, Sihvonen, P, Skou, P, 2019. Volume 6. Part 1. Subfamily Ennominae II: (Boarmiini, Gnophini, additions to previous volumes). Brill, Leiden" title="Volume 6. Part 1. Subfamily Ennominae II: (Boarmiini, Gnophini, additions to previous volumes)." year="2019">
<normalizedToken id="F8208A6D227FA9CB88D6AAE3C893985A" originalValue="Müller">Mueller</normalizedToken>
et al. (2019)
</bibRefCitation>
treated this claim as a formal synonymy of 
<taxonomicName id="1493A5B36E838AC276102754C0762D94" genus="K." lsidName="K. insignata" pageId="0" pageNumber="52190" rank="species" species="insignata">
<emphasis id="57AFDF02676476A8E8DF548504A26757" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="52190">K. insignata</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
and 
<taxonomicName id="25920BB0C0325948E03F4CE623C5B766" genus="K." lsidName="K. menadiara" pageId="0" pageNumber="52190" rank="species" species="menadiara">
<emphasis id="87B44392C5E01BD84D132FC0CA247A78" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="52190">K. menadiara</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
and, subsequently, provided molecular and morphological evidence to justify elevating it back to species. 
<taxonomicName id="659A75420309D95FCC513E5B6DD9FAE3" authority="Hausmann, 1994" authorityName="Exposito" authorityYear="2005" class="Insecta" family="Geometridae" genus="Kuchleria" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Kuchleria garciapitai" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="0" pageNumber="52190" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="garciapitai">
<emphasis id="9C6A5DF6E7C98A128819A5006BB43AD2" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="52190">Kuchleria garciapitai</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
remains a junior synonym of 
<taxonomicName id="E872B70EEF41F590DA96577BF4B4AA64" genus="K." lsidName="K. insignata" pageId="0" pageNumber="52190" rank="species" species="insignata">
<emphasis id="D9AC534BBA5378A869560B8E15128AF0" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="52190">K. insignata</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
